lytically. The aim of this series\nof works is to apply our approach to the Divertor Tokamak Test facility (DTT),\nto be built in Italy, and to ITER.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Jun 2022 17:12:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2022 17:24:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
