e dynamical variety seen at the Jovian poles. Additionally,\nderived values of localized horizontal shear and Ld may constrain FFR formation\nand evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Jun 2022 22:52:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-20"}
