-Betti Torelli theorem for K3 surfaces over $\\overline\n\\mathds{Q}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Jun 2022 08:26:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2023 13:36:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-17"}
